snippet: Jang of South Korea shot a two-under-par 69 on Saturday, leaving her a stroke ahead with one round left in the L.P.G.A. Tour’s rain-plagued Marathon Classic in Sylvania, Ohio.
abstract: Ha Ha Jang takes lead heading into final round of LPGA Marathon Classic.
lead_paragraph: Jang of South Korea shot a two-under-par 69 on Saturday, leaving her a stroke ahead with one round left in the L.P.G.A. Tour’s rain-plagued Marathon Classic in Sylvania, Ohio.

headline.main: Ha Na Jang Leads Marathon Classic
